  body
    section#hero
      header
        .left
          a(href="/")
            img#logo(src="img/uxtools-logo.svg")
        .right
          ul
            li
              a(href="/tools") Tools
            li
              a(href="https://blog.uxtools.co") Blog
      .wrapper
        h1 The ultimate comparison of UX industry tools.
        p There's a new design tool every week. Someone had to step up and compare them all. Take a look and see how these design, prototyping, collaboration, and monitoring tools work for you.
        a(href="/tools" target="_blank")
          button See the Tools 
           include img/icons/arrow-right.svg
    section.light
      .wrapper.wide
        img.illustration(alt="illustration" src="img/illustration/toolbox-inbox.svg")
        h2 Straight from my toolbox to your inbox.
        p Companies like 
          a(href="https://adobe") Adobe
          | , 
          a(href="https://atomic.io") Atomic
          | , and 
          a(href="https://zurb.com") Zurb
          |  have reached out to show me their latest tools. Don't waste your time keeping up with tools. Let me do the work for you in one simple, monthly newsletter.
        //- Begin MailChimp Signup Form
        #mc_embed_signup
          form#mc-embedded-subscribe-form.validate(action='//uxtools.us14.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=56c88bcfa8f1dc80f5c401b3a&id=218467b99e', method='post', name='mc-embedded-subscribe-form', target='_blank', novalidate='')
            #mc_embed_signup_scroll
              //- label(for='mce-EMAIL') Subscribe to our mailing list
